      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/mujam-al-ahadith-al-mutabara:1:3:1",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/9/1/3/1",
      "text": [
        " : قال رسول الله صلى الله عليه وآله: فضل العلم أحب إلى الله من فضل العبادة وأفضل دينكم الورع"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "1. [1/9] al-Khisal: From his father (Ali b. al-Husayn b. Babawayh) from Ali from his father (Ibrahim b. Hashim) from Ibn Maymun from Ja’far b. Muhammad from his forefathers from Ali عليه السلام who said: the messenger of Allāh صلى الله عليه وآله said: the merit of knowledge is more beloved to Allāh than the merit of worship. The best of your religion is self-restraint (from sins)."
        ]
      }
    },
